title: A keynote: Life on Fire Conference
description: An oldie but goodie. Back when I was, let's say, a little less "in-shape" ;) But, this needs to be here. It's one of my all time greats. A lot of fire, truth, and hopefully value for you. Let me know what you think! Tweet me: @GaryVee.
